desc_short	-----								This is a novel puzzle game. It creatively asks you to control two people simultaneously. The game consists of three charpters and the levels become more and more difficult. Its a perfect game to exercise your brain. 这是个新颖的解谜游戏，它创造性的要求您同时控制两个角色。游戏共分三章，关卡会逐渐变难。对于锻炼您的大脑，这是款非常好的游戏。							
